downloadTitle: Organizational Data in Microsoft 365 Template - with Skills
downloadDescription: Excel file template to support organizational data uploads in Organizational Data in Microsoft 365
detailsSection: Use this template for preparing your organizational data before uploading it from within the Organizational Data Upload in M365 feature in Microsoft Admin Center
systemRequirementsSection: The Organizational Data Upload in M365 feature is available via a web browser. The organizational data file can be prepared using excel to open the template and a text editor for the CSV file
installInstructionSection: Follow instructions on the template to prepare the organizational data in a CSV format.
